<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4505401>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. Xistrella dubia (Brunner von Wattenwyl, 1893).A – body of male, dorsal view; B – body of female, dorsal view; C – body of male, lateral view; D – body of female, lateral view; E – right antenna; F – head, dorsal view; G – head, frontal view; H – head and pronotum, lateral view; I – left fore femur, lateral view; J – left middle femur, lateral view; K – left hind femur, lateral view; L – left hind tibia, dorsal view; M – left posterior tarsi, lateral view. Scale bar = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4505401/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4505398>
    dc:description "Fig. 1. Morphology of Xistrella species. a – X. motuoensis Yin, 1984, body, lateral view; b – X. hunanensis Wang, 1999, body, lateral view; c – X. wuyishana Liang, 1991, body, lateral view; d – X. cliva Liang, 1991, body, lateral view.Drawings according to: a –YIN (1984); b – WANG (1999); c, d – ZHENG (1991)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4505398/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4505405>
    dc:description "Fig. 4. Xistrella hainanensis Deng, sp. nov., female, holotype: A – body, dorsal view; B – body, lateral view; C – head and pronotum, lateral view; D – head, frontal view; E – head, dorsal view; F – head, lateral view; G – right antenna; H – left fore femur, lateral view; I – left middle femur, lateral view; J – left hind femur, lateral view; K – left posterior tarsi, lateral view; L – subgenital plate, ventral view. Scale bar = 1 mm" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4505405/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

